            <title>[GROOVY-6522] implicit invocation not working for member closures when using @CompileStatic annotation</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-6522</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Originally discussed here: &lt;a href=&quot;http://stackoverflow.com/questions/21149013/groovy-implicit-invocation-not-working-for-member-closures-when-using-compilest&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://stackoverflow.com/questions/21149013/groovy-implicit-invocation-not-working-for-member-closures-when-using-compilest&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

